snippet.title: Uprooted Trailer
snippet.description:
**Updated trailer as of 1/24/20


A 2D platformer that explores themes of assimilation common to immigrant narratives—how much must be sacrificed in order to progress through the world?


A Gameheads Summer 2019 Project.
Follow the dev team on Twitter @BiqsyDevTeam for updates!
